  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK765">
<l>kūṟṟuṭaṉṟu mēlvariṉuṅ kūṭi yetirniṟku</l>
<l>māṟṟa latuvē paṭai</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>That indeed is an army which is capable of offering a united resistance, even if Yama advances against it with fury.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
